- **GitHub**: https://github.com/jiripech/ta-cukrarna

## Project Purpose & Goals

- **Type**: Responsive web application (PWA)
- **Purpose**: Basic information website for bakery "Ta Cukrárna"
- **Inspiration**: Simplicity like Instagram or Google Photos
- **Features**:
  - Progressive content management by user
  - Image upload and gallery management
  - Push notifications (opening hours changes, news)
  - Offline functionality (PWA)

